highlights.text: The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “One Of The Girls (with JENNIE, Lily Rose Depp)” is the highest at #4.
“ONE CALL” by Rich Amiri is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 106 spots at #76.
“lovely (with Khalid)” by Billie Eilish and Khalid has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 303 weeks straight.
“Bandit” by Don Toliver is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #83.
